'''植发'''是指经过测试需要接受[[頭髮|頭髮]]的移植位置适合种植头发后，通过使用特殊的[[器械|器械]]将头发的[[毛囊|毛囊]]与周围部分的组织完整地切取下来，使其脱离头皮原来的位置，然后移植到需要种植头发的位置的一系列[[医学|医学]]操作。<ref>{{cite web|title=An Update on Diagnosis and Treatment of Female Pattern Hair Loss|url=https://www.medscape.com/viewarticle/810613_12|website=Medscape Logo|access-date=30 May 2018|archive-date=2017-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171008212452/http://www.medscape.com/viewarticle/810613_12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Medscape">{{cite web|last1=Singhal|first1=Hemant|title=Wound Infection Medication|url=https://emedicine.medscape.com/article/188988-medication|website=medscape|access-date=30 May 2018|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125174031/https://emedicine.medscape.com/article/188988-medication|dead-url=no}}</ref>

